10 ða ic ongeat ðæt min neb wæs gehefegod
11 ðurh ðone sciman micle ma ðonne ær,
12 and ða ungewunelican ðing me wæron wundor;

19 ðam ðe ofstigð, and swa fela tosceð
20 fram ðæs stanes hryre on gelicum ryne,
21 swa swa geswutelað gefylsta and cræft;

22 swa ðuhte me ðær beforan me
23 of leohte gebrocenum beon perced;
24 for ðon wæs min gesiho hræd to fleonne.

40 Min lareow and ic sylfa twegen
41 uppe eodon; and ic ðohte, ða ic eode,
42 ðæt ic mihte sumne sped on his wordum findan;

52 Ac gif ðæs hehstan heofontungles lufu
